But the implications of such a shift to market approaches go well beyond the fact that <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Poland</ENAMEX> is already working on nationwide emissions trades to reduce smelter pollution , or that the <ENAMEX TYPE="NORP">Soviets</ENAMEX> plan to introduce marketable pollution permits in some <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">republics</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">next year</ENAMEX> .
