<ENAMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">One</ENAMEX> participant prematurely declared that <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">America</ENAMEX> has had a free market in goods but a planned economy for environmental protection , while <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Poland</ENAMEX> represents the opposite .
